c: 22
v: 18
t: "Do you not see that to God bow down 薑in submission襁혻all those in the heavens and all those on the earth, as well as the sun, the moon, the stars, the mountains, the trees, and 薑all襁 living beings, as well as many humans, while many are deserving of punishment. And whoever God disgraces, none can honour. Surely God does what He wills"